OL,3,CWe go inside the Severn Tunnel as it
OL,4,Ccloses for major renewal work
OL,6,FTrains from South Wales to the West of
OL,7,FEngland and beyond are rerouted via
OL,8,FGloucester while the tunnel is shut.
OL,10,FNick Millington, Network Rail's Route
OL,11,FDirector for Wales & Borders, tells me
OL,12,Fabout the complexity of managing the
OL,13,Ftunnel.
OL,15,F"It's an incredible feat of
OL,16,Fengineering. It's 7000 meters long and
OL,17,Ffor many years was the longest tunnel
OL,18,Fin Great Britain. It does take care
OL,19,Fand attention and we've got a number
OL,20,Fof different things going on in this
OL,21,Ftunnel at any one time."
