OL,3,CWe go inside the Severn Tunnel as it
OL,4,Ccloses for major renewal work
OL,6,F"We've got a 25,000 volt power
OL,7,Fdistribution system overhead that
OL,8,Fpowers the trains. We've got the track
OL,9,Frailway system below, drainage, and
OL,10,Fwe've got signalling equipment and the
OL,11,Fstructure of the tunnel itself.
OL,13,F"It does take a lot of inspection and
OL,14,Fa lot of care to keep the railway safe
OL,15,Fand operational down here."
OL,17,FPowerful pumps keep the tunnel from
OL,18,Fflooding.
