OL,3,CWe go inside the Severn Tunnel as it
OL,4,Ccloses for major renewal work
OL,6,FThe result is that track that would
OL,7,Fnormally have a life of 25 years has
OL,8,Fto be replaced every ten instead.
OL,10,F"We appreciate we've got the railway
OL,11,Fblocked... is an inconvenience for
OL,12,Fpassengers for the 16 day period" he
OL,13,Fsays.
OL,15,F"But it is fundamental to the way in
OL,16,Fwhich we manage the infrastructure
OL,17,Fdown here.
OL,19,F"By the time we're finished, we'll see
OL,20,Fthe entirety of this line through the
OL,21,Ftunnel renewed from end to end."
