OL,3,CWe go inside the Severn Tunnel as it
OL,4,Ccloses for major renewal work
OL,6,FThe tunnel is a vital link between
OL,7,FSouth Wales and England.
OL,9,FKeeping it operational requires
OL,10,Fconsiderable effort, resource and
OL,11,Fplanning.
OL,13,FBut its continued survival is a
OL,14,Ftestament to the skill of the
OL,15,FVictorian engineers who constructed
OL,16,Fit, and the teams tasked with
OL,17,Fsupporting it now.
